    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的目标</strong>是逃离太空站——穿过破损的走廊，重新启动被遗忘的系统，并在潜伏的变异怪物中生存。找到最后一艘可用的飞船——你回到地球的唯一希望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306380/extras/58ba81dfb94e53957778763a3c63b90f.poster.avif?t=1749582736\" width=608 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306380/extras/58ba81dfb94e53957778763a3c63b90f.webm?t=1749582736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306380/extras/58ba81dfb94e53957778763a3c63b90f.mp4?t=1749582736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306380/extras/9794e2d9ca93c8aa7b29d2ce2bafe424.poster.avif?t=1749582736\" width=608 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306380/extras/9794e2d9ca93c8aa7b29d2ce2bafe424.webm?t=1749582736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306380/extras/9794e2d9ca93c8aa7b29d2ce2bafe424.mp4?t=1749582736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306380/extras/f858a818e1004994efc67c361660b535.poster.avif?t=1749582736\" width=608 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306380/extras/f858a818e1004994efc67c361660b535.webm?t=1749582736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306380/extras/f858a818e1004994efc67c361660b535.mp4?t=1749582736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306380/extras/0c426331590e5f150edf511818401bc9.poster.avif?t=1749582736\" width=608 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306380/extras/0c426331590e5f150edf511818401bc9.webm?t=1749582736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306380/extras/0c426331590e5f150edf511818401bc9.mp4?t=1749582736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br>你醒来了。你又变回了人类。但能维持多久？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Twice Dead</strong>是一款叙事驱动的第一人称生存恐怖游戏。你在一个废弃设施中醒来，变异怪物在走廊游荡，这个世界——还有你——都出了问题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不记得自己是怎么到这里的。你不知道为什么你的样貌不同。你唯一的希望是逃离这里，回到地球。但每走一步都会带来新的问题：<br><strong>你在哪里？这里发生了什么？你到底怎么了？</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔍 主要特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔪 战术生存战斗</strong><br>用有限的资源和简陋的武器对抗扭曲的生物。每场战斗都至关重要——决定何时战斗，何时逃跑，何时牺牲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🧠 叙事与环境谜题</strong><br>无过场动画或冗长解释。通过游戏世界发现故事。解决融入叙事的物理谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🚪 探索推动故事发展</strong><br>每个房间和走廊都藏有线索。无任务标记——依靠你的直觉和求生欲望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🌌 失重幻觉</strong><br>受太空站生活启发的动作与设计——但有些地方令人毛骨悚然。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🧟 智能敌人</strong><br>敌人会记住你。有的追捕，有的逃跑。你永远不知道下一步会发生什么。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🎮 极简界面</strong><br>无完整HUD或小地图。一切都是世界的一部分。生存依赖观察和直觉。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧩 游戏概览</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>类型：</strong> 第一人称射击 | 生存恐怖 | 解谜冒险</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>时长：</strong> 8–15小时（取决于探索和难度）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重玩性：</strong> 多条路径选择，动态谜题与隐藏背景故事</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎧 音效与氛围</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态音景，响应你的行动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高品质3D音效，增强沉浸感和决策体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐稀少出现，但强烈且难忘</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 平台与支持</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全面支持手柄</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >优化键盘与鼠标操作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面向PC（Windows）发布</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >语言：英语，阿拉伯语，法语（更多即将上线）</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >❓ 游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无引导——每一次发现都属于你</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无传统教程、任务或对话树</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界让你去<i>感受</i>故事，而非仅仅观看</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结局颠覆你所认知的一切</p></li></ul>",
